NVMeAgent(8) System Manager's Manual NVMeAgent(8)

NAME

NVMeAgent — Agent for NVMe devices.

SYNOPSIS

NONE (launched by launchd)

DESCRIPTION

NVMeAgent allows the system to to present notifications related to NVMe devices.

This command is not intended to be invoked directly.

FILES

/usr/libexec/NVMeAgent
 

SEE ALSO

launchd(8)

HISTORY

The NVMeAgent utility first appeared in MacOS 10.13.

January 18, 2017 MacOS
